    "description": "BASAULT VR is a virtual reality movement shooter. Run, jump, swing around on your grappling hook and shoot with a variety of complex yet familiar firearms. Use those tools to survive and reach the end of this roguelite!<br><br>*WARNING: do not play if you are prone to motion sickness*<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/81c7b52954ac26762a91a410a4930933.poster.avif?t=1697460378\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/81c7b52954ac26762a91a410a4930933.webm?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/81c7b52954ac26762a91a410a4930933.mp4?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/b4d27807976f12b90c6f92638684448f.poster.avif?t=1697460378\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/b4d27807976f12b90c6f92638684448f.webm?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/b4d27807976f12b90c6f92638684448f.mp4?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>WAIT... WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO BE DOING?</u><br><br>This game is a roguelite. Your goal is to survive a series of hand designed arenas against tough ennemies with your mobility and weaponry and reach the end of the cycle to unlock new Etheral Weapons!<br><br>_________________________________________________________________________________________________________<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/fb80a1bfc234a4116e5e2725768175cd.poster.avif?t=1697460378\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/fb80a1bfc234a4116e5e2725768175cd.webm?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/fb80a1bfc234a4116e5e2725768175cd.mp4?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>...ETHERAL WEAPON? WHAT'S THAT?</u><br><br>An Etheral Weapon is a special type of gun that you can always spawn from behind your hips. Whether your gun is empty, you dropped it off a cliff or you just want to dual wield because that's the kind of <i>cool dude</i> you are, you can pull out these single magazine weapons to get you out of a bind!<br><br>_________________________________________________________________________________________________________<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/dc161eee54b9a322def554934a6c4172.avif?t=1697460378\" width=620 height=310 /></span><br><u>18 UNIQUE ARENAS...</u><br><br>...made for the sole purpose of shooting, running and swinging around in.<br><br>_________________________________________________________________________________________________________<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/ebf6bcf6f74ceeaecf6ddbdca048531d.poster.avif?t=1697460378\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/ebf6bcf6f74ceeaecf6ddbdca048531d.webm?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/ebf6bcf6f74ceeaecf6ddbdca048531d.mp4?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>10 UNIQUE GUNS...</u><br><br>...and more to come. Enjoy the entirely physical reloading and handling!<br><br>_________________________________________________________________________________________________________<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/f0d9e71a7c24666e2be9e79f595d5030.poster.avif?t=1697460378\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/f0d9e71a7c24666e2be9e79f595d5030.webm?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823830/extras/f0d9e71a7c24666e2be9e79f595d5030.mp4?t=1697460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>THANK YOU</u><br><br>Making this game alone would be quasi-impossible if it wasn't for the help of these people and ressources. Please look them up and give them some love by clicking on &quot;Visit the website&quot; on the sidebar :)",
